hey guys  one of the main reasons I run scoops is because I am running  a 
much larger engine in my 59 panel. 1904cc with dual 40 dells.  as the  vents 
were designed for a 1200cc motor with a singe 28 pict carb. with the  larger 
motor and carbs more air is required.  They did lower the oil temps  about 
8 degrees. best thing that worked for me lowering the oil temps was using  
the porsce 912 gen pulley and installing a type 4 oil cooler.  these 2  items 
lowered the oil temps about 15 degrees.  later  mark  d
